    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monsters and Magics is a casual online card game meant to be played with friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > New and familiar mechanics inspired by classic card games combine to create a unique experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle the computer or your friends to earn new cards and build stronger decks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 300 cards you can build a variety of decks with different ways play and win.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play online with friends through Steam or LAN</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle against 10 computer controlled opponents with different play styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 300 unique cards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monster Summoning mechanic lets you play powerful cards from your deck and hand</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action point system used to keep turns shorter and decision making important</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start every game with your chosen Field card enabling synergies and combos while guiding deck building</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock all cards in game by playing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn in game money to buy any card</p></li></ul>",
